m Long)","Powered Endocutter Reloads (Staple Leg Length)":"MECRW (2.5mm White), MECRB (3.5mm Blue), MECRGD (3.8mm Gold), MECRG (4.1mm Green), MECRT (4.4mm Black)","Trio Reloads (Stapler Size Inner to Outer)":"Vascular Medium (White): 2.0-3.0mm; Medium Thick (Purple): 3.0-4.0mm; Extra Thick (Black): 4.0-5.0mm","MIRUS Linear Cutter (MLC Series)":"MLC60 (64mm Staples line, 60mm Cut), MLC80 (84mm Staples line, 80mm Cut), MLC100 (104mm Staples line, 100mm Cut); Rows: 4, Staples: 64/84/104","MIRUS Auto Linear Stapler (MALS Series)":"MALS30 (11 staples, 2 rows), MALS45 (15 staples, 2 rows), MALS60 (21 staples, 2 rows), MALS90 (33 staples, 2 rows); Lengths: 3.5mm (Blue) / 4.8mm (Green)","MIRUS Circular Stapler - III Rows (Variants)":"MCS-21R3 (Cut 12mm, Head 21mm, 21 staples), MCS-24R3 (Cut 15mm, Head 24mm, 24 staples), MCS-25R3 (Cut 16mm, Head 25mm, 27 staples), MCS-26R3 (Cut 17mm, Head 26mm, 33 staples), MCS-29R3 (Cut 20mm, Head 29mm, 36 staples), MCS-31R3 (Cut 21mm, Head 31mm, 36 staples), MCS-32R3 (Cut 22mm, Head 32mm, 42 staples)","MIRUS Hemorrhoids Stapler (PPH)":"MPPH32 (32mm, 2 rows, 32 staples), MPPH34 (34mm, 2 rows, 32 staples), MPPH34R3 (34mm, 3 rows, 48 staples), MPPH36R3 (36mm, 3 rows, 48 staples); Closed staple height: 0.75-1.6mm","MERINEUM Mesh Technical Matrix":"Pore Size: 1.8-2 mm; Pre-Absorption Weight: 185 gsm; Post-Absorption Weight: 40 gsm; Thickness: 0.5-0.6 mm; Initial Burst Strength: 350 N","MERIGROW Mesh Technical Matrix":"Material: Polypropylene; Pore size: 1.5-2.3 mm; Weight: 55 gsm; Burst strength: 98.06 N/cm2; Thickness: 0.60 mm","MESIC Laser Ablation Technical Data":"Laser Type: GaAiAs Diode; Wavelength: 1470nm; Max Power: 12W; Pulse Duration: 10us - 3s; Repetition: 1 Hz-20KHz; Weight: 2.1 Kg","PROFOUND Mesh Fixation Spikes":"MFD15A/MFD15N (15 spikes), MFD30A/MFD30N (30 spikes); Tube diameter: 5 mm; Length: 36 cm"},"brand":"MIRUS","parent_brand":"Meril","description_shadow":"A comprehensive suite of advanced surgical tools including powered and manual endoscopic staplers, titanium mechanical stapling devices, composite and macroporous hernia meshes, energy-based resection systems, and handheld robotic articulation devices for minimally invasive surgery.","division_shadow_original":"Endo Surgery","shadow_product_id":"986c031e7ada75c1","shadow_source_files":["Endo P2 Product Range.pdf"],"shadow_source_pages":["9"],"shadow_sku_count":3,"source_of_truth_fields":{"slug":"live","images":"live","status":"live","seo_meta_title":"live","seo_meta_description":"live","brochure_url":"live","pack_size":"live","size_variables":"live","description_live":"live","technical_specifications":"live","brand":"shadow","parent_brand":"shadow","description_shadow":"shadow","shadow_source_files":"shadow"},"enriched_from_shadow":true,"mapping_confidence":"high","review_required":false,"match_method":"family_brand_division","match_score":1,"catalog_created_at":"2026-03-27T16:50:59.716888+00:00","semantic_anatomy_scope":[],"semantic_brand_system":"MIRUS","semantic_coating_default":null,"semantic_confidence":0.95,"semantic_conflict_codes":[],"semantic_enriched_at":"2026-03-27 18:04:20.338000","semantic_implant_class":"staplers","semantic_material_default":null,"semantic_parent_brand":"Meril","semantic_review_required":false,"semantic_rule_hits":["MIRUS_STAPLER_001"],"semantic_system_type":"stapler_system","clinical_reclassified_at":"2026-03-27 18:21:25.378000","clinical_subtitle":"MIRUS by Meril","clinical_indications":["Laparoscopic Ventral Hernia Repair","Incisional Hernia Repair","Parastomal Hernia Repair","Umbilical Hernia Repair","Peritoneal Defect Closure","Open & Laparoscopic Inguinal Hernia Repair","E-TEP procedure","TAPP | TEP | ROBOTIC TAPP","EVLT/Varicose Vein","Fistula and Hemorrhoid procedures","Pilonidal sinus and Fissure treatment","General, Colorectal, and Oncology surgery","Gastroenterology and Thoracic surgery"],"materials_canonical":"Titanium (Staples, Spikes, and Fixation Alloy)","features_list":["Extra flexibility: Up to 60 degrees of maximum reach on Powered Endocutters","Optimal Tissue Management System with Trio stepped reloads","Dual side firing with safety lock for Linear Cutters","Staple compression gauge to ensure accurate formation across variable tissue thickness","Tissue Compression Indicator on Hemorrhoids stapler for proper B-shaped staple formation","Synthetic Absorbable Anti-adhesive PLCL barrier resorbs between 90-120 days","Advanced RTTI II Algorithm for rapid transaction in Ultrasonic shears","Fully articulated 7 Degrees of Freedom (DOF) on HandX robotic system","Optical entry trocars for tissue layer visualization during insertion"],"brochure_intelligence_updated":true}}]
